setDetails.setDescription:
The NFT Index is a capitalization-weighted index that tracks the performance of decentralized financial assets across the market.
The NFT Index aims to track projects in Decentralized Finance that have significant usage and show a commitment to ongoing maintenance and development.
Streaming Fee - every month 50% goes to buy $GNFT (GOVERNANCE TOKEN for nftindex.tech, more info you can find on site)
setDetails.managerDescription: The NFT Index by https://nftindex.tech/ is a digital asset index designed to track tokens performance within the NFT industry.
